data.description: Superb Central Valley Rancher w/ 4+ beds, 2 baths, spacious modern kitchen, open layout, full basement, large garage/shop, positioned on a huge 0.27 acre quiet lot with double gate RV parking and fenced garden area. This beauty has a cooks kitchen with newer stainless appliances, abundance of counter and cabinet space with built in custom pantry & coffee bar with custom concrete counters! Updated baths and newer flooring. Fully finished basement with additional rooms – great space for family or guests! Efficient gas forced air heating and central A/C. Shop/garage is large with updates and has built in chicken coop & storage on back end. Located in highly rated CV schools, shopping & easy access to I-90. Newer roof and low maintenance siding. Custom rock and concrete work inside and out with custom concrete patios. Large fenced yard with garden. Home Warranty included. Assumable 2.25% Interest Rate – Must See!
